        "so_what_text": "The drive for attainment and aspirational approach to presentation has allowed the school to make steady progress against national benchmarks. \n\nThe collective work of departments to implement interventions and review attainment data allows for success in almost all subjects and departments session after session, with a majority of departments continually demonstrating a positive trend for course comparator values in Insight.",
