        "so_what_text": "The collated evidence highlights the key role of The Pupil Improvement Team in the school. Young people are actively involved in decision-making processes and work closely with the school community to share, and collaborate on, school improvement.  Our young people can articulately share strengths and next steps to support school improvement. The feedback from the Pupil Improvement Team is used to support school improvement priorities.",
